{"tid":715150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【23歲女自殺倫常慘劇】白馬嘯西風呢單野，蘋果記者根本就想將輿論推向連登","createTime":"2018-06-24T09:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T00:09:05.000Z","uid":160807,"like":25,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1429a3d475be57ebf5333c08d641c89be993d460","tid":715150,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"觀察左好耐，唔講唔得<br />\n<br />\n觀察返白馬嘯西風單野，報紙佬由第一日開始就想塑造出係網上討論區叫佢自殺既負面形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本就想將輿論指向連登，妖魔化連登仔<br />\n<br />\n睇返之前個報導，多次刻意提及連登<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/If95HC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FIf95HC.png&h=45744b8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/9szimu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F9szimu.png&h=0c7d29d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/jPW5fn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FjPW5fn.png&h=9a366cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個人自殺有好多原因，有好多野收收埋埋，個原因從來都唔係外人形容得簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家報紙佬就刻意簡化成件事原因係濕疹困擾　＝＞　上連登　＝＞　自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未有連登之前咪又係大把人自殺，就算冇連登呢個平台，都有facebook、instagram、高登、香討，如果死者沉迷facebook，係咪就可以話facebook導致佢自殺？<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報facebook留言<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/bKLBaA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FbKLBaA.png&h=60ca361b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/fkOjJ1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FfkOjJ1.png&h=d1de2fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後一句，白馬嘯西風RIP，願你來生不做香港人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母蘋果日報</span></span>"},{"pid":"4c2b5104efaad25f27ba256e73e44788674a6893","tid":715150,"uid":50275,"like":16,"dislike":7,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T09:17:21.000Z","msg":"連登污煙瘴氣就認左佢啦"},{"pid":"60bcfc888c159146983e86c7496623fc86f6f1c5","tid":715150,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"冇啦<br />\n上連登會自殺就唔止佢一個啦<br />\n<br />\n會自殺所以上連登又好難駁佢"},{"pid":"5338ce9cf1e448d5377ef85ea8862b264153ce79","tid":715150,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60bcfc888c159146983e86c7496623fc86f6f1c5","tid":715150,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"冇啦<br />\n上連登會自殺就唔止佢一個啦<br />\n<br />\n會自殺所以上連登又好難駁佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"就正如自殺既人都會玩facebook<br />\n<br />\n唔等於玩facebook會自殺"},{"pid":"d7b049c32e95e9940a7c916d1d8f097786f54fe0","tid":715150,"uid":41308,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T12:28:58.000Z","msg":"佢都係講上連登訴苦<br />\n<br />\n諗多左"},{"pid":"954ec5d18b5dbd7e587f1ecb325bd0f954e9cef6","tid":715150,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"都係敘述事實啫"},{"pid":"f9b8be9c559ef66e98671f653ad090cd17cfd34c","tid":715150,"uid":31841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"咁連登係低質呀嘛<br />\n抵俾人屌喎"},{"pid":"a4af610b7c7499ee60928d68b8eb7057f610902b","tid":715150,"uid":122585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T00:09:05.000Z","msg":"大部份連登仔D言論遲早會害死人,今次仲害死三件。"}]}